Package org.jtrim2.image.async

Class IIOReadUpdateAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.jtrim2.image.async.IIOReadUpdateAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventListener, IIOReadUpdateListener
public class IIOReadUpdateAdapter extends Object implements IIOReadUpdateListener
Defines a convenient base class for IIOReadUpdateListener implementations when you only want to implement some of its methods.

All the implemented methods of IIOReadUpdateAdapter does nothing but return immediately and subclasses may override them for their purpose.

Thread safety

Since the methods of IIOReadUpdateAdapter does nothing, they are safe to be accessed from multiple threads. Subclasses of IIOReadUpdateAdapter are not required to be safe to be accessed by multiple threads concurrently.

Synchronization transparency

Since the methods of IIOReadUpdateAdapter does nothing, they are synchronization transparent. As a listener interface, subclasses of IIOReadUpdateAdapter are not required to be synchronization transparent but should return reasonably fast.
